snippet.title: Met Gala 2014 Power Couples: Beyonce & Jay Z, Kim & Kanye, Johnny Depp & Amber Heard
snippet.description:
Subscribe to TheShowbiz411! http://bit.ly/1dXOPuV
Some of Hollywood's hot couples hit the red carpet at the Metropolitan Museum of Art Costume Institute annual gala in New York on Monday. Regulars Beyonce and Jay Z, both dressed in Givenchy Haute Couture, proved they're still crazy in love when the rapper slipped a ring back on his wife's finger after it fell off while posing for pictures. David and Victoria Beckham looked dressed to impress with matching monochrome outfits. Vogue magazine's recent cover models, Kim Kardashian and Kanye West also turned the evening into date night. Report by Sarah Kerr.
